<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#4a0e0e">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
    
    <title>Under Maintenance — Thikana Dhabla Ghosi | Badgujar Rajput Heritage</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Thikana Dhabla Ghosi website is currently under maintenance. We are polishing the royal halls and will return shortly. Please check back soon.">
    
    <link rel="icon" href="1200.jpeg">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;1,500&family=Cinzel:wght@500;600;700&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Tiro+Devanagari+Hindi&family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --wood: #2B1810; --wood-deep: #1C0F0A; --lac: #7A1F1F; --lac-deep: #5C1717;
            --gold: #C99A3A; --gold-bright: #E8C166; --gold-pale: #F0D68A;
            --sand: #F2E8D5; --paper: #E8DCC4; --paper-light: #F7F1E4;
            --smoke: #4A3C2C; --ash: #9C8D76;
            --display: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; --display-decorative: 'Cinzel Decorative', cursive;
            --eyebrow: 'Cinzel', serif; --body: 'Lora', serif; --devnag: 'Tiro Devanagari Hindi', serif;
            --shadow-elevated: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            --transition-smooth: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: var(--body); color: var(--smoke); background: var(--sand);
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(122, 31, 31, 0.05) 1px, transparent 0);
            background-size: 24px 24px; line-height: 1.7;
            min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        .ribbon { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 5px; background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #FF9933 0px, #FF9933 20px, #FFFFFF 20px, #FFFFFF 40px, #138808 40px, #138808 60px); opacity: 0.5; z-index: 10; }

        .maintenance-container {
            max-width: 620px; margin: 40px 20px; text-align: center;
            background: var(--paper-light); border: 1px solid #d6c39a; border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 50px 40px; position: relative;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-elevated);
        }
        .maintenance-container::before {
            content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--gold), var(--gold-bright), var(--lac), var(--gold-bright), var(--gold));
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }

        .maintenance-icon {
            font-size: 5rem; margin-bottom: 8px;
            animation: hammerFloat 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes hammerFloat {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(-5deg); }
            75% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(5deg); }
        }

        .maintenance-title {
            font-family: var(--display); font-size: 2.2rem; color: var(--wood);
            margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700;
        }
        .maintenance-subtitle {
            font-family: var(--eyebrow); font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--lac); margin-bottom: 18px; text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .maintenance-divider {
            width: 80px; height: 2px; background: var(--gold);
            margin: 0 auto 22px; position: relative;
        }
        .maintenance-divider::before, .maintenance-divider::after {
            content: "◆"; color: var(--lac); position: absolute; top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 0.5rem;
        }
        .maintenance-divider::before { left: -18px; } .maintenance-divider::after { right: -18px; }

        .maintenance-message {
            font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--smoke); margin-bottom: 14px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .maintenance-hindi {
            font-family: var(--devnag); font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--lac);
            margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 600;
        }
        .maintenance-estimate {
            font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ash); font-style: italic;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            padding: 10px 18px; background: rgba(201,154,58,0.08);
            border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block;
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,154,58,0.2);
        }

        .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 18px; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 40px;
            text-decoration: none; font-family: var(--eyebrow); font-size: 0.72rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-weight: 600; transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-bright));
            color: var(--wood-deep); box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(201,154,58,0.3);
        }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }

        .progress-bar-wrap {
            margin: 25px auto 0; max-width: 350px;
        }
        .progress-label {
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
            font-family: var(--eyebrow); font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            color: var(--ash); margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%; height: 6px; background: var(--sand);
            border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,154,58,0.3);
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%; width: 65%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-bright), var(--lac));
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: progressPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes progressPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.7; }
        }

        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 28px; padding: 16px 20px;
            background: rgba(201,154,58,0.05); border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,154,58,0.15);
            font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--ash); line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .contact-info a { color: var(--lac); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .contact-info a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: var(--gold); }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .maintenance-container { padding: 35px 22px; }
            .maintenance-title { font-size: 1.6rem; }
            .maintenance-icon { font-size: 3.5rem; }
            .maintenance-subtitle { font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>


    <div class="maintenance-container">
        <div class="maintenance-icon">🔨</div>
        <div class="maintenance-title">Under Maintenance</div>
        <div class="maintenance-subtitle">Polishing the Royal Halls</div>
        <div class="maintenance-divider"></div>
        
        <p class="maintenance-message">
            Our digital fortress is undergoing restoration work. Like the great forts of Rajputana, we believe in keeping our walls strong and our halls worthy of the Badgujar legacy.
        </p>
        <p class="maintenance-hindi">॥ क्षमा करें, वेबसाइट रखरखाव के लिए अस्थायी रूप से बंद है ॥</p>
        
        <div class="maintenance-estimate">
            ⏳ Estimated Time: We'll be back shortly — please check again soon
        </div>

        <div class="progress-bar-wrap">
            <div class="progress-label">
                <span>Restoration Progress</span>
                <span>65%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-row">
            <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn btn-primary">🔄 Refresh Page</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
            <p>📧 For urgent inquiries, contact us at: <a href="mailto:info@thikanadhabla.in">info@thikanadhabla.in</a></p>
            <p>🏰 Thikana Dhabla Ghosi — Shajapur, Madhya Pradesh</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 6px; font-family: var(--devnag); color: var(--gold-bright);">॥ जय माँ आसावरी — राघवाय नमः ॥</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>